      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/47/18",
      "text": [
        " \"لاَ تَصْلُحُ وَ لاَ لَبَنُ اِبْنَتِهَا اَلَّتِي وُلِدَتْ مِنَ اَلزِّنَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4678 - Ali ibn Ja'far asked his brother Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) about a woman who committed adultery - whether she is suitable to be taken as a wet nurse.\nHe (as) replied: \"She is not suitable, nor is the milk of her daughter who was born from adultery.\""
        ]
      }
    },
